{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_10_01_short",
  "title": "白石沙季 1話 恋愛についての勉強 (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "……ふぅ\nお疲れ様です、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Phew.\nGood work‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様、沙季\n今日のライブも大盛り上がりだったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work‚ Saki.\nToday’s live was a huge success too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "ファン参加型の歌唱ライブでしたから\n一体感があって、私も楽しかったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since it was a fan-participation singing live‚\nit had a sense of unity‚ and I really enjoyed it too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "余韻に浸りたいところではありますが\n明日の仕事のためにも今日は早めに上がらないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’d like to savor the afterglow‚ but—\nI need to wrap up early for tomorrow’s work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "明日は月ストのみんな別々の仕事ですよね\n琴乃ちゃんはラジオで、すずちゃんは雑誌の撮影で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tomorrow everyone in Moon Tempest has different jobs‚ right?\nKotono-chan has radio‚ Suzu-chan has a magazine shoot…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.5000020345
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "さすがは沙季だな。みんなのスケジュールも\n頭に入っているだなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As expected of Saki. You’ve even memorized\neveryone’s schedule too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.9565437064,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "みんながどんな仕事をしているのかを\n把握しておくのは大事ですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s important to know what work\neveryone is doing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.0333353679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.6666687012
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "本当は休ませてあげたいんだが\nBIG4になってからますます注目されていてな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I really do want to let you rest‚\nbut ever since you became BIG4‚ the attention has only grown…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.8666687012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "心配しないで下さい、まだまだ平気です\nむしろもっと頑張れますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t worry. I’m still perfectly fine.\nIf anything‚ I can work even harder.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.833334605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.533334605
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "それに、こうして仕事をこなしていくことで\n私達が活躍する姿をファンに届けることが出来ます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And by steadily doing this work‚\nwe can show our fans us at our best.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.3000012716,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}